{
  "texts": [
    "The coding sequence was cloned into pCAMBIA-1302.",
    "The Arabidopsis overexpression lines were conducted and generated by A. tumefaciens GV3101 mediated transformation [92].",
    "Three biological replicates were used, and the experiments were performed three times.",
    "Primer sequences are given in Additional file 1: Table S23.",
    "All Arabidopsis genotypes were grown at 22 °C (day/night) under long-day conditions (16-h light/8-h dark)."
  ]
}